title: Sibling Watchery - Drag Race All Stars Season 7 - Episode 6
description:
Bob and Monét review Drag Race All Stars Season 7 Episode 6 as the queens live out their Y2K fantasies on a dragtastic tribute to TRL! And on the runway, category is: Night of 1,000 Dolly Partons. Pop star Tove Lo joins the judges' panel.
